<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>파티 예약 확인</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="reservation-container">
        <h1>파티 예약 확인</h1>
        
        <div class="reservation-info">
            <h2>예약 정보</h2>
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>선택한 날짜:</strong> <span id="selectedDate"><%= selectedDate %></span></p>
                <p><strong>상품 ID:</strong> <span id="productId"><%= productId %></span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="customer-info">
            <h2>예약자 정보</h2>
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>이름:</strong> <span id="customerName"><%= memberInfo.name %></span></p>
                <p><strong>연락처:</strong> <span id="customerPhone"><%= memberInfo.phone %></span></p>
                <p><strong>이메일:</strong> <span id="customerEmail"><%= memberInfo.email %></span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reservation-form">
            <h2>추가 정보</h2>
            <form id="reservationForm">
                <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= productId %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="selectedDate" value="<%= selectedDate %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="name" value="<%= memberInfo.name %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="phone" value="<%= memberInfo.phone %>">
                <input type="hidden" name="email" value="<%= memberInfo.email %>">
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="gender">성별</label>
                    <select id="gender" name="gender" required>
                        <option value="">선택하세요</option>
                        <option value="male">남성</option>
                        <option value="female">여성</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">요청사항 (선택)</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="요청사항이 있으면 입력해주세요"></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <div class="payment-info">
                    <h3>결제 정보</h3>
                    <div class="bank-info">
                        <p><strong>입금 계좌:</strong> 국민은행 123456-78-901234 (주)미터파티</p>
                        <p><strong>입금 금액:</strong> <span id="totalAmount">65,000</span>원</p>
                        <p><strong>입금자명:</strong> <span id="depositName"><%= memberInfo.name %></span></p>
                    </div>
                    <p class="payment-notice">* 예약 확정 후 24시간 이내에 입금해주세요.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group agreement">
                    <label class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="agreementCheck" required>
                        <span>개인정보 수집 및 이용에 동의합니다.</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
                
                <div class="button-group">
                    <button type="submit" id="confirmButton">예약 확정</button>
                    <button type="button" id="cancelButton">취소</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="successModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">&times;</span>
            <h2>예약이 완료되었습니다</h2>
            <p>예약 정보가 이메일로 발송되었습니다.</p>
            <p>입금 계좌: 국민은행 123456-78-901234 (주)미터파티</p>
            <p>입금 금액: <span id="modalAmount">65,000</span>원</p>
            <p>입금자명: <span id="modalName"><%= memberInfo.name %></span></p>
            <button id="goHomeButton">확인</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="/js/reservation.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 